Headline: Near.ai is founded
Text: Named for the science fiction novel "The Singularity Is Near" by Ray Kurzweil, Illia Polosukhin and Alexander Skidanov start Near.ai in late 2016 to explore program synthesis.

Headline: Near.ai pivots to Near Protocol
Text: Researching program synthesis led the team to explore programmable smart contract platforms and crypto payments in late 2017 and early 2018 and Near Protocol was born.

Headline: Near Protocol raises pre-seed round
Text: SV Angel helps Near obtain the initial capital to begin making Near Protocol a reality.
